org.cove.jade.util
Class GVector

    java.lang.Object
    org.cove.jade.util.GVector
public class GVector
extends java.lang.Object

Class implementing a 2D geometric vector, consisting of two numbers that represent X and Y co-ordinates, and the ability to perform vector manipulation and operations. Note that in Flade, this was called a "Vector" but we can't call it "Vector" in JADE as Java already has a vector class that we use (java.util.Vector), which represents a variable length array-like data structure.
